          <dl>
            <dt>404 on /dev/*</dt><dd>these routes are dev-only. Run <code>npm run dev:{SITE}</code>, not <code>preview</code>.</dd>
            <dt>no galley to review</dt><dd>start one with <code>{`/editorial-draft-review --site ${SITE} <slug>`}</code>.</dd>
            <dt>iterate doesn’t trigger</dt><dd>the agent has to run <code>/editorial-iterate</code>. The browser button just marks the workflow; Claude does the writing.</dd>
